<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT87">
<l>imaiyap perumalaipō lintiraṉārk kiṭṭa</l>
<l>camaya viruntuṇṭār kāppār camayaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṭā ṉavaikāppāṉ kārkkaṇṭaṉ nāṉmukaṉō</l>
<l>ṭuṇṭā ṉulakō ṭuyir.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who is [the Lord] who protects [the cowherds], having eaten</l>
<l rend="indent">the conventionally established feast</l>
<l>served for Indra, [heaped up] like the big Himalayan mountains?</l>
<l>[It is] He who has seen the [different] creeds, He who protects them,</l>
<l>He who swallowed the worlds along with living beings</l>
<l rend="indent">as well as the black-throated [Śiva and] the four-faced [Brahmā]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
